{"type":"message","id":"a5ceb4a5","parentId":"1a5dab50","timestamp":"2026-03-06T12:17:31.906Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"41\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"495506013\",\n  \"sender\": \"Matteo Cicalese\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-06 12:17 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Matteo Cicalese (495506013)\",\n  \"id\": \"495506013\",\n  \"name\": \"Matteo Cicalese\",\n  \"username\": \"CicaMatt\"\n}\n```\n\ndifference between skills and tools in openclaw"}],"timestamp":1772799451905}}
{"type":"message","id":"dcd7a155","parentId":"a5ceb4a5","timestamp":"2026-03-06T12:17:36.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_040a9a3297cf14d40169aac5dccba48191a0e29bf155d619e9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpqsXdPBaGPZ5f3FEmRAOOJ0dwwHbpuCOdfLhs4c3t29liJhEnvqRL5Xkbs67vcsCYtA_EsLUim2XqdZis3rNDOgwd0mptCxSTXZFdnvKqXGA3-HcFYB83liLSBt1jtN1OsKqbJK5ThZc0ywwZUjp6kqweEeRyPcKAt37wuFShuKDYZmkzJlV-79Oiz5M8e-fn1BjX60Uv5Zvi7hOgTm19FMBvt-6XQr8n2fY2IjKqNVMPRUX386Di4en4g5dk2WOT6ky8Nlv8yYCRi_dsY0BKBThhYdt2qIAyNP5vr5JsHZvYvB6PJBlCF8x2WV9dHEcg7z8LLw0CysigNtambqEMOa4Z-JOYs7XimHYoXuVUlTpS4avZdcAHh7EAtzxzW9-EMDiFc8OdReZlRr2xeMkRU27ZWTB6u_Wiovht94IR0mGa2HI8WY4B6VbYzO2YlhsVzZ5Y2CltiP_hzzkoa31AmzkT6ULjgUNi04bJAFtARonQNqnR0C324uAelMi9e2pUxJtwSHdna9SfYAB1vaNiVeC5VFKqrS3SKLwqBDk3FI6e5aoTtXvFnp-emBWU1yIZzxaQ1FLHawHFTtwyYO3qkJtiH2wRAJ3guEudNoA_KJBZoFJZpsKeFuOFuEgZ4J4EEq4kcmbi_yWHdrj8kduSUo-X2bNU9gFAnok2_FW_0MotsQh3brDl5jTEMS3J0fL_VQOUOnGiaWYywwosXpsXznsEhn578SSKXmuJV2ZuheKHP132CuR9h9HTgX-tdRPciUGMyPaPLZmZNZFKn6IGq99lovg3dF0hpPIBPEItbAck2f6EhkEZ6fiE0NBTa2vgbyPn-MV8qQdbgu8V4AjNrFJElESamB6fxC8j5MnngJFMHNXzgRIp4js5ixnYRIKntTpE\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Great question. In OpenClaw:\n\n- **Tools** = the **capabilities/actions** the agent can execute  \n  (e.g., send a message, read a file, check session status, call APIs, run commands).\n\n- **Skills** = **instruction bundles** that tell the agent **how to do a type of task well**  \n  (playbook + best practices + sometimes scripts/assets).\n\nQuick mental model:\n- **Tool = hands**\n- **Skill = technique**\n\nExample:\n- Weather **tooling** might fetch forecast data.\n- `weather` **skill** tells the agent when to use wttr/Open-Meteo, how to format output, and what not to do.\n\nSo: tools are raw power; skills are guided behavior on top of that.","textSignature":"msg_040a9a3297cf14d40169aac5dd20c88191bde0ef2d3e94f071"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":357,"output":183,"cacheRead":7296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7836,"cost":{"input":0.00062475,"output":0.002562,"cacheRead":0.0012768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00446355}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772799451905}}
