{"type":"message","id":"d2ec2bd0","parentId":"de91676d","timestamp":"2026-03-06T12:18:23.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Providing concise OpenClaw guidance**","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_040a9a3297cf14d40169aac60b64208191b7bfb004535888e9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpqsYM9fqr6GTLPqAaOKjRXEamXU4BHKfLzuVmKKDtnxt9TmTGxBYaNaBaaHpCcsvjnE8ABPZmOKcj4ufqAw_ySQ9i_WBldio9Zz7vyThg8EaU6KwFuhzGjIs__SnbLAPK_D0loW8tvbjyHEWytRkq5yGqNM30j-vG3JwGJDkHAqZtowCkIVqezj4DQvB2Mo8zd4WR10aJkMKAAfp9NtFSFGWPTXdDZYSg0ag4M-DsgTpM0iJaQXKAOZpuquRBOlh8aOqPr4SscpS_7PrCVLPeywtxLCCjI9rcnmKWrCq7zHtpy6q0ZAK5XBByIY8uOMqKziCep3lgDIfljT0QCYEsTkiv6Z7vBoa9lSRKlHFOzSvHArbLA0HQHsjiCDJ64x0z7M21au7CHvQk_JaoWGpcE6pkyECIZcO8UMygKi5RxRp03_PiDoIz9tEpASD0kRTmvCfNR7zHvJluwkKBEbEUT7WsFgwCmLf6wLvCKzv9ZuA-71n37WVSfBSCUkBf7hJ1P21l9IdPa9dACVNrrWkyT_uno_zaf5rkzCeUd3Ru8-oA3mkrtDmyJAcM58IWg1UHTIullN066tYujDkprIaMGgLcDjK7SrTJkIl8asI75SpGJ6CRiPffCNiBK_mtBF7Gq1wQDj6pM7JhPtm2v6QNtCNliuB5qXhdSm6knJg4WZcsItYPPGc3XUuRcGFbam_fyNueuXHNyPd9yFE9yY7qe4WqS9EUIaARTMWMH_i607ASU0ghFNiXlXP9rMXSqSYwpXArHtYv1laXcAaMobkdEUrqGmq4JDeh3Aj6NHZ8Ju7g3a-bjCAjK4Pat8yLDPuiY0ck60TBQMrLpCQVMzwgGXqZPFkiZm_G-E-D1CUvjYON7M-wuyXJvdr12XA8LwkBT0yvOcJ57-woRgGupPHSkIDWK1PKqLcAn7TwieaGfgSsilRNxxuDSqjbdb639IFbKaJULBStM6LnucYUUZfoVQUiMQ==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Providing concise OpenClaw guidance**\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yes — absolutely.\n\nIn practice, in OpenClaw you usually do this in one of two ways:\n\n1) **Custom Skill (recommended first)**  \n- Package instructions + scripts that call your endpoint  \n- Great when you want reusable behavior without changing core runtime\n\n2) **Native Tool integration (deeper/custom runtime work)**  \n- Add a first-class tool so the agent can call it directly  \n- Best for stable, frequently used capabilities\n\nFor your endpoint use case, start with a **Skill** unless you need low-latency, strict schemas, or broad reuse across agents.\n\nIf you want, I can scaffold a minimal custom skill for:\n- `POST /your-endpoint`\n- auth header support\n- JSON input/output contract\n- basic error handling + retry rules","textSignature":"msg_040a9a3297cf14d40169aac60c27708191a940f83a0d95e728"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":413,"output":196,"cacheRead":7552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8161,"cost":{"input":0.00072275,"output":0.002744,"cacheRead":0.0013216,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00478835}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772799498085}}
